{"type": "article", "id": 24828, "title": "灯泡灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153255jnFEa3Dtv9wC4dLs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏灯是最原始的灯泡形状，希腊设计师 Yiannis Ghikas 想要设计一个最简单原始的灯来代表天才的想法。它的灯座是一圈黄铜，上面刻着像自行车车把手一样的菱形纹，在圆形灯泡的对比下它显得精致而古典，也冲淡了原本极简形状的单调。<a href=\"http://www.yiannisghikas.com/?ds-gallery=grip-lamp-for-creaid-2016\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153254txcS8VQe9fl60bvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 281px; width: 375px; left: 575px; top: 229px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153254NemaOu3pj8lVRB7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}